text: The Parliament of Ivory Coast is the legislature of Ivory Coast. From 1960 to 2016, it was a unicameral body. It became a bicameral body after a new constitution was approved by referendum on October 30, 2016. The new parliament is made up of two chambers: *The Senate (Upper Chamber) *The National Assembly (Lower Chamber) ==References== Category:Government of Ivory Coast Ivory Coast Ivory Coast
title: Parliament of Ivory Coast
